data.description: This 4 bedroom home offers 2247sf of living space that includes a partially-finished basement. Wood floors in the living room, dining room, and all four bedrooms. The living room has a wood burning fireplace, sellers never used and a large, picture window. The dining room offers built-in hutches and French doors to the 3-season sunroom. The eat-n kitchen offers shaker style cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and LVT flooring. A pantry and half bath are located off the kitchen. There is also a man-door to the rear yard. Upstairs offers 4 bedrooms, all with wood flooring. At the top of the stairway is a linen closet and the primary bedroom with 2 closets. Then a French door opens to the 3 additional bedrooms and a walk-up attic. The full bath has a tub/shower combo with tile surround, and LVT flooring.  The partially finished basement has the second fireplace. Laundry and HVAC are on the unfinished side with updated electric panel and 2 additional storage rooms. Preapproved buyers are welcome by appointment only. Must provide preapproval or proof of cash funds.
